sition: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">您</span><span style="font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">保证其检举事项的真实性、公正性，同时尊重</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">叮当电商公司</span><span style="font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">及本网站对被检举事项的处置措施；</span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">被检举用户有权通过专门的客服途径进行辩解，但不影响</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">叮当电商公司</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Arial; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 10.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">或本网站先行采取相应措施，</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋